mg src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"182fd81d66c71a1346d52faf87a56e7ca69a2337","tid":1506833,"uid":45910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T06:15:12.000Z","msg":"支持警察執法就去買餸煮飯啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f47c3a217a1a11440645518b0e233450a0f3af3","tid":1506833,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T06:43:13.000Z","msg":"等佢地食多啲咪仲好"},{"pid":"409c4af72ef766cf1c562e2565c7421cf850a5e9","tid":1506833,"uid":109433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T06:45:48.000Z","msg":"警嫂加餸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89f774229b5407a0f3b2ffb829d7cb998420da7e","tid":1506833,"uid":278154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T08:07:03.000Z","msg":"【8.25 荃葵青遊行：街市內施放催淚彈】<br />\n昨日的遊行最終在黃昏時演變武力清場，警方施放大量催淚彈沿途驅趕示威者。期間警方亦向楊屋道街市內發放了催淚彈，雖然楊屋道街市屬半開放式街市，但當時地面樓層經已下半閘，故並非通風良好的開放環境。地下樓層售賣海鮮，故催淚氣體很可能同時污染食材及儲水，令街市內商戶損失慘重。<br />\n據聞其後有區議員要求食環署派員立即到場清潔該處，食環署職員大約晚上7時到場處理，相信當時街市內的催淚氣體仍未散去，而街市外的街道則氣氛緊張，警方與示威者仍在對峙。<br />\n攝：Benjamin Yuen@ USP United Social Press 社媒<br />\n#USP20190825"},{"pid":"a4d5865b58b42781f3d75b4e6cc3637f694113f0","tid":1506833,"uid":278154,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T08:16:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tZm6sGC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtZm6sGC.jpg&h=e315a033&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}